title: Logger Pro 3
description:
Since there were no working Logger Pro 3 torrents for the mac on this site, I decided to take it upon myself to find a version- licensed- and share it with you guys.

Thank you, thank you, no need to clap.





Just choose which version you want by ticking either the pkg file, the exe file, or both. I assume you already found a way to get the windows one, but it's included as well.

Password is included, none of that take a survey to get password BS.
